name: Sampler Pack
description: For the indecisive pup that wants a taste of each cookie before committing to a larger single flavor package. Inside are 2 banana cookies, 2 pumpkin cookies & 2 greek yogurt cookies to test out on their tastebuds. Cookie bases in this pack are Whole Wheat Flour & White Rice Flour

name: Banana Cookies
description: Our banana cookie was created for pups with a love for peanut butter and banana. Blue agave nectar is added to sweeten the cookies without adding sugars or preservatives. Cookie base is Whole Wheat Flour

name: Pumpkin Cookies
description: Our pumpkin cookie was created for pups with weight issues. The pumpkin is beneficial to your dog's digestive health to help keep them at their ideal weight. Spinach is added to pump your pup full of extra vitamins and iron. Blue agave nectar is added to sweeten the cookies without adding sugars or preservatives. Cookie base is Whole Wheat Flour

name: Greek Yogurt Cookies
description: Our greek yogurt cookie was created for pups with sensitive stomachs and/or allergies. The greek yogurt helps with their digestive and immune system health, while the honey helps with pollen and other outdoor allergies. Added is a hint of mint to freshen their breath. Cookie base is Gluten Free White Rice Flour

name: Rolled Oats Cookies
description: Our rolled oats cookie was created for pups with a sweet tooth. The apple and blueberries help clean residue off their teeth while proving them with a good source of antioxidants and fiber. Rolled Oats are added to pump your pup full of extra vitamins and protein. Honey adds a bit more sweetness and helps with pollen and other outdoor allergies. Cookie base is Gluten Free White Rice Flour
